Further this result implies that the stationary part of the wind—which satisfies the ideal MHD condition, and which may be subject to charge starvation, satisfies 23\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
